#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.46"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.46:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.46:0.2"
msgid "5. Attadīpavagga "
msgstr "5. Be Your Own Island "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 46. Dutiyaaniccasutta → dutiyaaniccatāsuttaṃ (bj) | aniccatā 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.46:0.3"
msgid "46. Dutiyaaniccasutta "
msgstr "46. Impermanence (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.46:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.46:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, form is impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn22.46:1.3"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering. "

msgctxt "sn22.46:1.4"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā; "
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.46:1.5"
msgid "yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
msgstr "And what’s not-self should be truly seen with right understanding like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.46:1.6"
msgid "Vedanā aniccā … "
msgstr "Feeling is impermanent … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.46:1.7"
msgid "saññā aniccā … "
msgstr "Perception is impermanent … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.46:1.8"
msgid "saṅkhārā aniccā … "
msgstr "Choices are impermanent … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.46:1.9"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "Consciousness is impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn22.46:1.10"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering. "

msgctxt "sn22.46:1.11"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā; "
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.46:1.12"
msgid "yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
msgstr "And what’s not-self should be truly seen with right understanding like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.46, sc2
msgctxt "sn22.46:2.1"
msgid "Evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passato pubbantānudiṭṭhiyo na honti. "
msgstr "Seeing truly with right understanding like this, they have no theories about the past. "

msgctxt "sn22.46:2.2"
msgid "Pubbantānudiṭṭhīnaṃ asati, aparantānudiṭṭhiyo na honti. "
msgstr "Not having theories about the past, they have no theories about the future. "

#. VAR: thāmaso → thāmasā (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn22.46:2.3"
msgid "Aparantānudiṭṭhīnaṃ asati, thāmaso parāmāso na hoti. "
msgstr "Not having theories about the future, they don’t obstinately stick to them. "

#. VAR: Thāmase → thāmasā (bj, s1-3, km) | thāmaso (mr)
msgctxt "sn22.46:2.4"
msgid "Thāmase parāmāse asati rūpasmiṃ … "
msgstr "Not misapprehending, the mind becomes dispassionate towards form, "

msgctxt "sn22.46:2.5"
msgid "vedanāya … "
msgstr "feeling, "

msgctxt "sn22.46:2.6"
msgid "saññāya … "
msgstr "perception, "

msgctxt "sn22.46:2.7"
msgid "saṅkhāresu … "
msgstr "choices, "

msgctxt "sn22.46:2.8"
msgid "viññāṇasmiṃ cittaṃ virajjati vimuccati anupādāya āsavehi. "
msgstr "and consciousness; it’s freed from defilements by not grasping. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.46:2.9"
msgid "Vimuttattā ṭhitaṃ. Ṭhitattā santusitaṃ. Santusitattā na paritassati. Aparitassaṃ paccattaññeva parinibbāyati. "
msgstr "Being free, it’s stable. Being stable, it’s content. Being content, they’re not anxious. Not being anxious, they personally become extinguished. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.46:2.10"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.46:2.11"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
